tensive barbecue menu in the country. The menu included Certified Angus Beef steaks, tender chicken, award-winning lamb ribs, and mouth-watering sides like Hickory Pit Beans and Cheesy Corn Bake.", photoCount: "704.0", ratingHistogram: "{\"count1\": 23, \"count2\": 68, \"count3\": 342, \"count4\": 999, \"count5\": 2573}", website: "http://www.jackstackbbq.com/?olonwp=z17TA_tz20aL5UmKf8LjMg", rankingPosition: "9.0", hours: "{\"weekRanges\": [[{\"open\": 660, \"openHours\": \"11:00\", \"close\": 1230, \"closeHours\": \"20:30\"}], [{\"open\": 660, \"openHours\": \"11:00\", \"close\": 1260, \"closeHours\": \"21:00\"}], [{\"open\": 660, \"openHours\": \"11:00\", \"close\": 1260, \"closeHours\": \"21:00\"}], [{\"open\": 660, \"openHours\": \"11:00\", \"close\": 1260, \"closeHours\": \"21:00\"}], [{\"open\": 660, \"openHours\": \"11:00\", \"close\": 1260, \"closeHours\": \"21:00\"}], [{\"open\": 660, \"openHours\": \"11:00\", \"close\": 1320, \"closeHours\": \"22:00\"}], [{\"open\": 660, \"openHours\": \"11:00\", \"close\": 1320, \"closeHours\": \"22:00\"}]], \"timezone\": \"America/Chicago\"}", address: "101 W. 22 St Freight House, Kansas City, MO 64108", neighborhoodLocations: [], dishes: ["Sandwiches", "Ribs", "Shrimp", "Salad", "Wings", "Carrot Cake", "Baby Back Ribs", "Salmon", "Beef", "Lamb", "Pork", "Onion Rings", "Baked Potato", "Sausage", "Coleslaw", "Brisket", "Cake", "Fried", "Potato Salad", "Cornbread", "Baked Beans", "Beef Ribs"], reviewTags: "[{\"text\": \"cheesy corn\", \"reviews\": 461}, {\"text\": \"jack stack\", \"reviews\": 676}, {\"text\": \"beans\", \"reviews\": 408}, {\"text\": \"burnt ends\", \"reviews\": 1029}, {\"text\": \"ribs\", \"reviews\": 622}, {\"text\": \"carrot cake\", \"reviews\": 108}, {\"text\": \"onion rings\", \"reviews\": 145}, {\"text\": \"prime rib\", \"reviews\": 117}, {\"text\": \"beef\", \"reviews\": 165}, {\"text\": \"cole slaw\", \"reviews\": 95}, {\"text\": \"ham\", \"reviews\": 49}, {\"text\": \"bread\", \"reviews\": 55}, {\"