ques and process that creates perfect 'cue. Share-ables, soups and salads, specialty sandwiches, brisket burgers, and award-winning BBQ dinner plates make up a menu that features wood-fire grilling from top to bottom but still allows for enough variety to satisfy any customer's needs. A menu filled with so many great options can be difficult to highlight, but the \"best wings on the planet\" and \"burnt-end burger\" are a few favorites you'll surely be back again for.", photoCount: "944.0", ratingHistogram: "{\"count1\": 30, \"count2\": 48, \"count3\": 209, \"count4\": 632, \"count5\": 2523}", email: "servicedirectory494@gmail.com", website: "https://q39kc.com/locations/midtown-bbq/", rankingPosition: "3.0", hours: "{\"weekRanges\": [[{\"open\": 660, \"openHours\": \"11:00\", \"close\": 1260, \"closeHours\": \"21:00\"}], [{\"open\": 660, \"openHours\": \"11:00\", \"close\": 1260, \"closeHours\": \"21:00\"}], [{\"open\": 660, \"openHours\": \"11:00\", \"close\": 1260, \"closeHours\": \"21:00\"}], [{\"open\": 660, \"openHours\": \"11:00\", \"close\": 1260, \"closeHours\": \"21:00\"}], [{\"open\": 660, \"openHours\": \"11:00\", \"close\": 1260, \"closeHours\": \"21:00\"}], [{\"open\": 660, \"openHours\": \"11:00\", \"close\": 1290, \"closeHours\": \"21:30\"}], [{\"open\": 660, \"openHours\": \"11:00\", \"close\": 1290, \"closeHours\": \"21:30\"}]], \"timezone\": \"America/Chicago\"}", address: "1000 W 39th St, Kansas City, MO 64111-3859", neighborhoodLocations: [], dishes: ["Sandwiches", "Pasta", "Burger", "Ribs", "Salad", "Wings", "Mac and cheese", "Pulled Pork Sandwich", "Salmon", "Beef", "Cassoulet", "Pork", "Beef Brisket", "Onion Rings", "Pork Belly", "Sausage", "Coleslaw", "Brisket", "Cake", "Fried", "Potato Salad", "Cornbread", "Baked Beans"], reviewTags: "[{\"text\": \"brisket\", \"reviews\": 949}, {\"text\": \"burnt ends\", \"reviews\": 816}, {\"text\": \"cassoulet\", \"reviews\": 58}, {\"text\": \"beans\", \"reviews\": 231}, {\"text\": \"apple salad\", \"revie